Fixpoint map_or (m0 m1 : Map bool) {struct m1} : Map bool := match m0, m1 with | M0, _ => M0 bool | _, M0 => M0 bool | M1 a0 b0, M1 a1 b1 => if Neqb a0 a1 then M1 bool a0 (b0 || b1) else M0 bool | M1 _ _, M2 _ _ => M0 bool | M2 _ _, M1 _ _ => M0 bool | M2 x0 y0, M2 x1 y1 => M2 bool (map_or x0 x1) (map_or y0 y1) end.
